# Symbolic Range Analysis

## Build
```bash
mkdir build && cd build
cmake -G Ninja ..
ninja
```

## Running the ESSAfier Pass
```bash
opt -load-pass-plugin=build/ESSAfier.so -passes="mem2reg,ESSAfier" -S tests/input.ll -o tests/output.ll
```

## Running the Symbolic Range Analysis
```bash
opt -load-pass-plugin=SymbolicRanges.so -passes="sra-annotator" -disable-output ../tests/test.ll
``` 
